title: Banyan Tree debuts its fourth hotel brand
text:
Banyan Tree debuts its fourth hotel brand 11 Hours Ago Ho Kwon Ping, executive chairman at Banyan Tree Group, says Banyan's recently launched hotel brand, Dhawa, caters to increasing numbers of Chinese middle-class, inbound travelers.
